reviewText: Los Angeles, 1991. It's been six years since Jack Deth (TIM THOMERSON) eliminated the last of the Trancers-those zombie-like creatures whose mission is murder. Jack has rebuilt his life in the present with his new wife Lena (HELEN HUNT) and has gotten rich in his commodities dealings with his old buddy Hap Ashby (BIFF MANARD), an ex-baseball hero.Now Jack's got that funny feeling again...he knows the Trancers are back. And there's more in store for him: Jack's first wife Alice Stillwell (MEGAN WARD),whom he thought dead, has been sent "down the line" to the present to help fight the new wave of Trancers. But she's lost somewhere in Los Angeles and Jack must find her. At the same time he must find and destroy Dr. Wardo (RICHARD LYNCH) the new leader of the deadly gang.Get ready for the ride of your life. TRANCERS II...it's the return of Jack Deth.

reviewText: The 5 discs in this set are the 5 movies starring Tim Thomerson as Jack Deth, a 6th movie was made, but only file footage of Jack Deth was used and it had a new, female lead.I remember back in the 1980's the ads that ran for Trancers - "Jack Deth is back.  And he's never been here before."  The series is a mixture of tongue in cheek horror/sci-fi and is of the sort that used to see good business at drive ins.Starring in the series are:Tim ThomersonHelen Hunt (yes THAT Helen Hunt)Art LaFleurTelma HopkinsBiff ManardMegan WardStacie Randalland a host of B movie actors.  Don't expect huge budgets or Oscar winning performances - just be ready to turn off your brain and be entertained.The movies are:Trancers (1985)Trancers II (1991)Trancers III (1992)Trancers IV (1994)Trancers V (1994)Included on the discs are behind the scenes and cast interviews.
summary: Jack Deth is back.  And he's never been here before.
